Arguments

data

data

...

passed as fun.arg to baseline_table()

by.var

specify stratification variable

add.p

add comparison/p-value

add.overall

add overall column

theme

set table theme

detail_level

specify detail level. Either "minimal" or "extended".

gtsummary table list object
